# ============================================
# Unity 项目 - 不应提交的自动生成/缓存文件
# ============================================
# 参考: https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Unity.gitignore

# Unity 核心缓存（体积大，会自动重新生成）
[Ll]ibrary/
[Tt]emp/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]ogs/
[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/

# 构建输出
[Bb]uild/
[Bb]uilds/
*.apk
*.aab
*.app
*.unitypackage
*.unitypackage.meta

# 日志和临时文件
*.log
.utmp/

# 内存捕获、录制（体积大）
[Mm]emoryCaptures/
[Rr]ecordings/

# IDE / 编辑器自动生成（Unity 打开时会重新生成）
*.csproj
*.unityproj
*.sln
*.suo
*.tmp
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db
.vs/
.consulo/
.gradle/
*.DotSettings.user

# Unity 崩溃报告
sysinfo.txt
mono_crash.*

# JetBrains Rider 插件
[Aa]ssets/Plugins/Editor/JetBrains*

# Visual Scripting 自动生成
[Aa]ssets/Unity.VisualScripting.Generated/

# 测试场景自动生成
[Ii]nit[Tt]est[Ss]cene*.unity*
ExportedObj/

# ============================================
# 通用 / 系统文件
# ============================================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ============================================
# 可选：若不想提交 AI 生成的示例脚本，可取消注释
# ============================================
# UnityProject/UnityTestProject/Assets/Scripts/Generated/
